{
  "id": "019cdcdc-fd01-7d11-b0d7-9ff93b03cd5f",
  "content": "## Fix\n\n### 1. Emit Resolvable `to_file` from Tree-sitter\n\n**File**: `crates/corvia-adapter-git/src/treesitter.rs`\n\n- `crate::foo::bar` now emits `CRATE_REF:crates/corvia-kernel/src:foo::bar` using `infer_crate_src_root()` to extract the crate's `src/` root\n- `super::foo` resolves relative to the source file's parent directory, also emitting `CRATE_REF` format\n- Fallback to `file_path` when resolution is impossible (e.g., `super` from crate root)\n- Added `infer_crate_src_root()` helper\n\n\n### 2. Multi-Strategy Target Resolution in `wire_pipeline_relations()`\n\n**File**: `crates/corvia-cli/src/main.rs`\n\nRewrote with `HashMap`-based file index and 4 resolution strategies:\n\n1. **Direct match**: `source_file == to_file` (handles \"implements\"/\"contains\" within same file)\n2. **CRATE_REF resolution**: `CRATE_REF:<root>:<module>` → try `<root>/<module>.rs` and `<root>/<module>/mod.rs`\n3. **JS/TS relative**: `./utils` → resolve relative to source file, try `.ts/.js/.tsx/.jsx` extensions\n4. **Suffix fallback**: match `to_file` as a suffix of known `source_file` paths\n\nAlso added self-edge filtering for \"imports\" relations.\n",
  "source_version": "docs/rfcs/2026-03-04-m4.2-graph-relation-wiring-fix.md",
  "scope_id": "corvia",
